---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About';
const description = 'About me';
const permalink = Astro.site 
  ? new URL('/about', Astro.site).href 
  : '/about';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="/assets/about-illustration.webp" alt="Illustration of a notebook" width="330">
      <figcaption>
        Illustration by
        <a href="https://icons8.com/illustrations/author/5c07e68d82bcbc0092519bb6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Icons 8</a>
        from
        <a href="https://icons8.com/illustrations" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ouch!</a>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>Hi there! I’m Samuel D. Jnr, a passionate full-stack web developer with a love for crafting clean, efficient, and impactful digital experiences. Whether it's bringing complex ideas to life or fine-tuning the smallest details, I enjoy working across the entire development spectrum.</p>

    <p>My journey into coding began with a curiosity for how the web works, and 
       the years, that curiosity has grown into a career. From front-end interfaces that captivate users to back-end systems that drive functionality, I thrive on building solutions that are both creative and practical.</p>

    <p>I believe that every project is an opportunity to learn, grow, and contribute something meaningful.</p>

    <p>Let’s connect! Feel free to check out my work on <a href="https://github.com/Sloane-J" target="_blank">GitHub</a> or drop me a line at <a href="mailto:samueldorkeyjr@gmail.com">samueldorkeyjr@gmail.com</a>. I’m always open to collaborations, new challenges, or just a good conversation about all things tech.</p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>


<style>
  .about-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .about-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }
  }
</style>
